  "text": "According to the International Agency for Research on Cancer there were about 13 % (1,825 thousand) of new lung cancer cases of the total number of new cancer cases and about 19.4 % (1,590 thousand) deaths of the total number of deaths owing to lung cancer in the world in 2012. In the structure of cancer pathology lung cancer takes first place for men and third place for women [CITATION_1] .",
